    "problemStatement": "Given two arrays AAA and BBB each of length NNN.\n\nFind the value \u2211i=1N\u2211j=1Nmax\u2061(Ai\u2295Bj,Ai&amp;Bj)\\sum_{i=1}^N\\sum_{j=1}^N \\max(A_i\\oplus B_j,A_i\\&amp; B_j)\u2211i=1N\u200b\u2211j=1N\u200bmax(Ai\u200b\u2295Bj\u200b,Ai\u200b&amp;Bj\u200b).\n\nHere \u2295\\oplus\u2295 and &amp;\\&amp;&amp; denote the bitwise XOR operation and bitwise AND operation respectively.\n\n\nInput Format\n\nThe first line of input contains a single integer TTT - the number of test cases. The description of TTT test cases follows.\nThe first line of each test case contains an integer NNN - the length of arrays AAA and BBB.\nThe second line of each test case contains NNN space-separated integers A1,A2,\u2026,ANA_1,A_2,\u2026,A_NA1\u200b,A2\u200b,\u2026,AN\u200b representing the array AAA.\nThe third line of each test case contains NNN space-separated integers B1,B2,\u2026,BNB_1,B_2,\u2026,B_NB1\u200b,B2\u200b,\u2026,BN\u200b representing the array BBB.\n\n\nOutput Format\nFor each test case, output the value \u2211i=1N\u2211j=1Nmax\u2061(Ai\u2295Bj,Ai&amp;Bj)\\sum_{i=1}^N\\sum_{j=1}^N \\max(A_i\\oplus B_j,A_i\\&amp; B_j)\u2211i=1N\u200b\u2211j=1N\u200bmax(Ai\u200b\u2295Bj\u200b,Ai\u200b&amp;Bj\u200b).",
    "constraints": [
      "1\u2264T\u22641051 \\leq T \\leq 10^51\u2264T\u2264105",
      "1\u2264N\u22641051 \\leq N \\leq 10^51\u2264N\u2264105",
      "0\u2264Ai,Bi&lt;2200 \\leq A_i, B_i \\lt 2^{20}0\u2264Ai\u200b,Bi\u200b&lt;220",
      "Sum of NNN does not exceed 2\u22c51052\\cdot 10^52\u22c5105 over all test cases."
    ],
    "inputFormat": "",
    "outputFormat": "",
